    "name": "全面战争：战锤3",
    "steam_appid": 1142710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/4399b64b745c1a2f0c3a90f5c8958dcd.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/868c3d11f98ec6a6d25501bded60d988.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>垂死的神明最后一声咆哮打破了世界之间的界限，开启了通向混沌魔域的传送门。恐虐、纳垢、奸奇、色孽，这四股毁灭之力从漩涡之中涌现了出来，它们四处散布着黑暗与绝望。<br><br>基斯里夫坚毅的勇士和幅员辽阔的震旦天朝就在风口浪尖之上，而一位恶魔亲王正在寻仇，他发誓要消灭那些腐蚀他的人。即将到来的风波将会吞噬一切。你会征服你的恶魔，还是让它们听令于你？ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/cb704e9e94a3a9f82c2795fa3a47d53c.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>你可以控制七个各具特色的种族以及数百种部队来打造一支军队，在那令人叹为观止的壮观世界里，纵横于史诗般的即时战斗之中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/53594a7d48dcf7a7ec302bb0addd31d1.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/f7005d773cb763558e117e4495dcca65.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>这是迄今为止最具雄心也是最具新意的《Total War》游戏，那引人入胜的叙事将让你代入到游戏之中，这会让你进入魔幻的混沌魔域之中，然后再回到凡世之中。在战略沙盒之中打造你的帝国，这沙盒之中每一场战役都是独一无二的。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/0d04020f1bac73bca6cdb2710c63d3f0.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/ca096cd20c8595f5e46d8c5e391f0cc5.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>有10位传奇领主可供扮演！你会选择站在混沌诸神的一边进行他们的恶魔战役，还是选择扮演震旦天朝的远古化形神龙？是与冰雪女王一起守护基斯里夫的冰封国度，还是扮演恶魔亲王来成为终极反派？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/0e90bfa944229bb57cd64e99e3720ecf.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/953e6a3b797e02253b64bab09565aab4.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>用海量的身体部件和力量定制你独一无二的恶魔亲王，你有无数种潜在的组合方式来配合你自己的游戏风格<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/694fe09d6942684f8f104b301ed29250.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/ad9631a5859bf15fa8b691a1bd7b3232.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>多人游戏的规模现在比以往更加庞大。混沌魔域的宏大多人战役可容纳8名玩家，还有紧张刺激的一对一君临模式，以基斯里夫和震旦为基础的剧情多人战役，还有排名与自定义战斗等等，想要与朋友来几场大混战，办法有的是。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142710/extras/344243864c93aecc3521c90c0528c6da.avif?t=1771415171\" width=616 height=344 /></span>",
